<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>QR Code Already Scanned</title>
<link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles.css"> <!-- Link to your CSS file -->
  <style>
    body {
    font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
    background-color: #f8d7da;
    margin: 0;
    padding: 20px;
  }
    h1 {
    text-align: center;
    color: #721c24;
  }
    .alert-container {
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    background: #f8d7da;
    padding: 20px;
    border: 1px solid #f5c6cb;
    border-radius: 5px;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
  }
    p {
    color: #721c24;
    text-align: center;
  }
    a {
    display: block;
    text-align: center;
    margin-top: 20px;
    color: #007bff;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: bold;
  }
    a:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
  }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
<h1>QR Code Already Scanned</h1>
<div class="alert-container">
  <p>The QR Code with ID <strong><%= qrCode.codeId %></strong> has already been scanned by <strong><%= qrCode.scannedBy %></strong> on <strong><%= qrCode.scannedAt.toLocaleString() %></strong>.</p>
  <p>Points Earned: <strong>10</strong></p>
  <a href="/scan">Scan Another QR Code</a>
  <a href="/generate">Generate New QR Code</a>
</div>
</body>
</html>
